name: MOBCOIN
description: MOBCOIN is the native token of the Crypto Gambinos NFT Project ecosystem. It serves as a governance token, allowing holders to participate in community decisions, and it also functions as an in-game currency within the family's business ventures. The token has a fixed supply of 777,777,777, symbolizing stability and community-driven growth. Additionally, there is a 5% utility fee on token sales, with 2.5% going to a liquidity pool and the other 2.5% to the family treasury, which is distributed quarterly.
